Ext.data.JsonP['Editors']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Editors</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p></div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-39685860\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Editors</h1>\n    <p>Studio uses different editors to modify files.  For example, Studio uses the TiApp editor to modify the <tt class=\" \">tiapp.xml</tt> file, and the Alloy XML View editor to modify all other XML files.  You can open up multiple editor, but only one can be active.  Each file type (or file) can be associated with different editors or an external program within Studio.    </p>\n    <p>Depending on the Editor, Studio may show warning and errors.  You can also add breakpoints for debugging in certain editors.    </p>\n    <p>If you do not want to open the file in its default editor, in the Project Explorer view, right-click the file, select <strong class=\" \">Open With...</strong>, then choose an Editor to open the file or <strong class=\" \">Other...</strong> to select from a list of Editors.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-39685860_Editors-Chapters\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Chapters</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"childpages-macro \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Navigating_Open_Files_with_Next_Editor_or_Previous_Editor\">Navigating Open Files with Next Editor or Previous Editor</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Modifying_Editor_Colors\">Modifying Editor Colors</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Changing_your_file_association_preferences\">Changing your file association preferences</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/39685860/Editors.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/39685860/Editors.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n        </img></p>\n    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=39685860\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Editors"});